THE 7 PORTFOLIO FEATURES

FEATURE 1 — Artifact hover tooltip
Hover within 20px of a moment dot → show small popup card (position:absolute within river zone):
- Phase label in phase color (8px uppercase)
- Moment title (10px, font-weight 500)
- Artifact type badges if photos attached
- Sub text
Below river: horizontal artifact timeline strip. Thumbnails with type label + date. "+" to add.

FEATURE 2 — Story blocks panel
Accessible via "Story blocks" toggle button in canvas bar.
Six block types with weight:
- "What changed" #8aab7e weight 30
- "Why it matters" #7b9cc4 weight 20
- "Human problem" #b88fc2 weight 20
- "Sudden constraint" #d4856a weight 15
- "Key decision" #9c8060 weight 10
- "Real quote" #9c9890 weight 5
Click blocks to place. Story completeness = sum of placed weights (0–100%), shown as thin progress bar.

FEATURE 3 — Story validator
Four status chips between river and artifact strip. Updates live:
1. Problem — green if has "observe" moment
2. Process — green if 3+ moments
3. Outcome — green if has "launch" moment
4. Decisions — green if any detail contains "not"
Colors: green (#eaf3de/#c0dd97/#27500a) · amber (#faeeda/#fac775/#633806) · red (#fcebeb/#f7c1c1/#a32d2d)

FEATURE 4 — Contribution view
Toggle "River" | "Contribution" in canvas bar.
Horizontal bar chart: noticed / proposed / decided / tested / presented.
Bars use phase colors. Below: auto-generated contribution signature paragraph.

FEATURE 5 — Voice calibration
See onboarding section above + account settings section 3.

FEATURE 6 — Always-editable showcase draft
In portfolio showcase: faded sentences (#b0ada6) = AI scaffolding. Full ink (var(--ink)) = owned by user.
Click sentence → contentEditable = true.
Track edits per project in localStorage.
Show "X% your voice" indicator.
Edits persist across sessions.

FEATURE 7 — Learning log + emerging POV
One learning per project. Written after project closes.
In sidebar: italic quote with project color left border.
In "For myself" showcase: learning block with project color left border.
If 2+ learnings exist: show "Emerging point of view" block at bottom of sidebar learning section.
Dark background (var(--ink)), generated synthesis in DM Serif Display italic, var(--bg) text.

