ACCENT HOOK (hooks/useAccent.js)

- On mount: read "fieldnotes_accent" from localStorage (default: "ink")
- Apply: document.documentElement.setAttribute("data-accent", accentId)
- Expose: currentAccent, setAccent(id)
- setAccent: saves to localStorage + applies data-accent attribute immediately
- Used in AccountSettings and App

