KEY BEHAVIORS

1. All borders are 0.5px — never 1px or 2px except left-border accents (2px) and active tab indicator (1.5px)
2. Accent color applies instantly on swatch click — no page reload needed
3. data-accent attribute lives on document.documentElement
4. Toast background uses var(--accent) so it always matches the current theme
5. "Portfolio" button, "+ moment" button, and all primary actions use var(--accent) background
6. Active tab indicator, active sidebar item, and selected phase pill all use var(--accent)
7. River curve stroke and fill also use var(--accent)
8. Phase dot colors on moments never change — they are always fixed phase colors
9. Account settings drawer slides in from the right with CSS transform transition
10. Settings drawer backdrop is semi-transparent and clicking it closes the drawer
11. Export data creates a JSON blob download named "fieldnotes-export-[date].json"
12. Reset to defaults: confirm → clear localStorage → reload page
13. localStorage save debounced 300ms for main state. Accent saves immediately (no debounce).
14. Voice calibration shows only if voiceProfile is null AND no projects in localStorage
15. Profile name (from account settings) appears in "For myself" showcase if set

