16. Build ShowcaseSelf.jsx
17. Build ShowcasePublic.jsx with depth switcher
18. Build ContribView.jsx
19. Build NewProjectModal.jsx and Toast.jsx
20. Test accent switching — all five accents, confirm river, buttons, tabs, sidebar all update
